code: public static SpatialStrategy readFromStream(StreamInput in) throws IOException {     return in.readEnum(SpatialStrategy.class). }
@Override public void writeTo(StreamOutput out) throws IOException {     out.writeEnum(this). }

public static SpatialStrategy fromString(String strategyName) {     for (SpatialStrategy strategy : values()) {         if (strategy.strategyName.equals(strategyName)) {             return strategy.         }     }     return null. }
